## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Run `npm run build` locally to verify that all module resolution errors are resolved.
- Verify that `prisma generate` has been run to ensure `apiCostEvent` and `logEntry` models are available.

### Manual Verification
- Check the `/api/finops/report` endpoint to ensure it returns valid data from the re-implemented [FinOpsIntelligence](file:///c:/Users/fmonf/Desktop/Software%20Enginnering%20LAPTOP/Agencia%2520B2B/agencia-web-b2b/src/lib/observability/finops/FinOpsIntelligence.ts#28-156) service.
